## Graphics as Expressions
Let's create a basic 2D plot:

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Type: Input
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Plot[x, {x, 0, 1}, PlotStyle -> (*VB[*)(RGBColor[1/2, 1/2, 1])(*,*)(*"1:eJxTTMoPSmNiYGAo5gUSYZmp5S6pyflFiSX5RcEsQBHn4PCQNGaQPAeQCHJ3cs7PyS8qYgCDB/bojA/2AO8aEYQ="*)(*]VB*)]

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Type: Output
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
(*VB[*)(FrontEndRef["b89e821b-86d6-4b7c-8eeb-e19b634765fe"])(*,*)(*"1:eJxTTMoPSmNkYGAoZgESHvk5KRCeEJBwK8rPK3HNS3GtSE0uLUlMykkNVgEKJ1lYploYGSbpWpilmOmaJJkn61qkpibpphpaJpkZm5ibmaalAgCI0hXv"*)(*]VB*)

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Type: Input
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
% /. {(*VB[*)(RGBColor[1/2, 1/2, 1])(*,*)(*"1:eJxTTMoPSmNiYGAo5gUSYZmp5S6pyflFiSX5RcEsQBHn4PCQNGaQPAeQCHJ3cs7PyS8qYgCDB/bojA/2AO8aEYQ="*)(*]VB*) -> Red}

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Type: Output
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
(*VB[*)(FrontEndRef["50a822fb-a4b9-4e97-95cd-5ab935120d87"])(*,*)(*"1:eJxTTMoPSmNkYGAoZgESHvk5KRCeEJBwK8rPK3HNS3GtSE0uLUlMykkNVgEKmxokWhgZpSXpJpokWeqapFqa61qaJqfomiYmWRqbGhoZpFiYAwCEdRV6"*)(*]VB*)

